\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
User Characteristic
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
As per the definitions given in 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sub:Definitions,-acronyms,-and"

\end_inset

 the respective applications are targeted to their respective markets: these consist of any citizen of the town for the customer-side applications, and of any recognized taxi driver for the taxi-side application.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Customers do not need specific competences to use the app other than a basic knowledge of web browsing (customers only) and of their mobile operating system (both customers and taxi drivers).
\end_layout

